OverHistory.NewCommentry: Ashleigh Gardner to Arundhati Reddy Wicket
OverHistory.Commentry: Ashleigh Gardner bowling to Arundhati Reddy, full length ball, pitching on leg stump, Arundhati Reddy plays a sweep shot WICKET Arundhati Reddy lbw Ashleigh Gardner (India (Women) 203 Runs for 9 wickets)
OverHistory.UPDCommentry:
WICKET! Ashleigh Gardner bowling to Arundhati Reddy, full length ball, pitching on leg stump, Arundhati Reddy attempting a sweep, misses it completely as the ball crashes into her front pad. Australia go up in unison, but the umpire isn't interested. After a quick discussion with Gardner, Tahlia McGrath opts for the review. UltraEdge confirms no bat involved, and ball tracking shows three reds—hitting leg stump! The decision is reversed, and Gardner celebrates a sensational five-wicket haul 

Arundhati Reddy lbw Ashleigh Gardner (India (Women) 203 Runs for 9 wickets)
